jot.manager.ai

Class AbstractPathFindersManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • jot.manager.ai.AbstractAI
      • jot.manager.ai.AbstractPathFindersManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PathFindersManager

    public abstract class AbstractPathFindersManager
extends AbstractAI
    Abstract class that each path finder must implement. Alternatively one massive class may be implemented instead.
    Author:
    G. Amador & A. Gomes
